Debug Segment-Triggered Flows
Test the behavior of your segment-triggered flows with the debug tool in Flow Builder.
This feature is available in Lightning Experience for Salesforce Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Marketing Cloud Growth edition.

In Flow Builder, click Debug to debug your flow.
